  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Sirmione in the summer is one of the prettiest towns on Lake Garda with a fairytale-like castle leading to quaint cobbled streets. It’s a renowned spa destination, using thermal waters that have been enjoyed since Roman times. It’s also a fantastic place to take a lakeside walk whilst sampling authentic gelato. With loads of gelaterie dotting the historic town centre, Sirmione serves some of the best ice-cream on the lake.</p>
<p><strong>Best for:</strong> easy walking, sightseeing</p>]]></listingDescription>
